Fourth Department,

May, 1975

(May 22, 1975) In the Matter of Westmoreland Teachers Association, Appellant, v Board of Education of the Westmoreland Central School District, Respondent.

Appeal unanimously dismissed, without costs, as moot, by reason of the expiration of the contract on June 30, 1974. (Appeal from part of order of Oneida Special Term denying application to confirm award of arbitrator.) Present—Moule, J. P., Cardamone, Simons, Goldman and Del Vecchio, JJ.
